metadata.name: Show me the way
metadata.description:
Falling asleep is the beginning of a new journey. Curiosity is always the potential for new beginnings. There are so many worlds that open up to you new possibilities and experiences, in which you can often lose your way if you don't carefully keep your inner compass.

Original painting. Oil on canvas. 
25 x 30 cm 
Year: 2021

NFT: 5553 x 4591 pixels  
Solovyova Anastasia
